## Installation

```bash
EMACSDIR=${EMACSDIR:-~/.emacs.d}
git clone --recursive https://github.com/yangg/emacs.d.git $EMACSDIR
# clean up
cd $EMACSDIR
echo "GNU Emacs" >> .git/modules/tomorrow-theme/info/sparse-checkout
cd tomorrow-theme
git config core.sparsecheckout true
git read-tree -mu HEAD
```
